application

Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.Controller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Initializable

    public class Controller
extends Object
implements Initializable
    Controller needs to implement Initializable as JavaFX relies on the class having an "initialize" method. It is going to execute the "initialize" method only AFTER the layout file has been loaded.
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    Captain Coder
    See Also:
    Initializable, Canvas, EventHandler
